{"type":"message","id":"3da667bb","parentId":"2fe7d650","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:49:28.436Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 15:49 UTC] So the purpose of the cron job and the orchestrator is to run every 15 minutes, and the main purpose of the orchestrator is to, through a round-robin work on, I think it runs every 15 minutes and it takes one channel at a time, and the goal is to help move the final of the conversation towards its purpose. So during the active hours, that means asking strategic questions. The questions could be filling in gaps, asking for status from the user, or anything like that. And in the off hours, it's thinking, it's organizing artifacts, running experiments, looking at patterns, looking at the previous day's activity, looking for weekly patterns, those kinds of things"}],"timestamp":1772466568434}}
{"type":"message","id":"7680f577","parentId":"3da667bb","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:49:35.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is describing a cron job and orchestrator system that:\n1. Runs every 15 minutes\n2. Uses round-robin to work on one channel at a time\n3. During active hours: asks strategic questions, fills gaps, checks status\n4. During off hours: organizes artifacts, runs experiments, analyzes patterns\n\nThis sounds like they want me to understand or possibly help set up/implement this system. Let me first check my memory to see if there's any prior context about this orchestrator or related work.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me check my memory for any prior context about this orchestrator system."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_515770464a734cb8a6586745","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"orchestrator cron round-robin channel strategic questions","maxResults":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7878,"output":151,"cacheRead":5888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13917,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772466568435}}
